%% Diagram: TLS 1.3 full handshake message flow (1-RTT)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server

    Note over C,S: Phase 1 — plaintext (necessary for key agreement)
    C->>S: ClientHello + key_share + supported_versions
    S->>C: ServerHello + key_share

    Note over C,S: Phase 2 — encrypted with handshake keys
    S->>C: EncryptedExtensions
    S->>C: Certificate (optional CertificateRequest)
    S->>C: CertificateVerify
    S->>C: Finished
    C->>S: Finished

    Note over C,S: Phase 3 — encrypted with application keys
    C->>S: Application Data
    S->>C: Application Data
